                In d<expan><ex>o</ex><abbr>m</abbr><ex>ino</ex></expan> bon<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>m<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>mori</abbr><ex>a</ex>e</expan> Aeliae Ka<lb break="no" n="2"/>lendin<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> fideli matri dulcissim<lb break="no" n="3"/>ae qui <note>sic</note> vixit annos <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>umero</ex></expan> LX Aelii M<lb break="no" n="4"/>ucianus Bassus Paulinian<lb break="no" n="5"/>us et Paulus <expan><abbr>fili</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> pientissimi <lb n="6"/>memoriam posuerunt
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Das Erhaltene ist in vier Teile gebrochen. Buchstabe A ohne Querhaste.</p>
